info.title: Template
info.description:
**Below is detail of each field for API Template** | Field | Type | Description | |---|---|---| | name | string | Name of Template | | category | array of object | Type of Category / Industry | | configuration | string | Stringify json detail of Flow Name and Pages | | description | string | Description of template | | createdTime | datetime | Template created time.
*format:* `Y-m-d H:i:s`,`Y-m-d\TH:i:s.vP`,`Y-m-d\TH:i:sP` | | updatedTime | datetime | Template updated time.
*format:* `Y-m-d H:i:s`,`Y-m-d\TH:i:s.vP`,`Y-m-d\TH:i:sP` |
